        "min": 10,
        "max": 5000,
        "value": 1500,
        "unit": "mm/s",
        "description": "Effective range for 1064 nm cleaning on plaster; slower speeds (500-1000 mm/s) for heavy contamination, faster (2000-3000 mm/s) for light. Recommended 1500 mm/s balances efficiency and safety. Source: Industry standards from Laser Cleaning Europe guidelines and equipment manuals (e.g., Adapt Laser Systems)."
      },
