        "min": 1,
        "max": 10,
        "value": 2,
        "unit": "passes",
        "description": "Single pass for light contamination, multi-pass (2-5) for heavy layers on plaster to gradually remove without damage. Recommended 2 passes for uniform results in industrial settings. Source: Industry case studies, e.g., restoration projects in Constr. Build. Mater. (2020)."
